{"tid":2499673,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"BLM遊行中出言侮辱亞裔警察 非裔男子被起訴要求道歉賠償","createTime":"2021-04-22T05:25:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-22T08:13:46.000Z","uid":28765,"like":303,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":90,"replies":[{"pid":"b8c4b1f1be7ca2a219bdd4edbdbe82ae19ab41a1","tid":2499673,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T05:25:22.000Z","msg":"紐約市警探工會（Detectives Endowment Association）民事起訴一名非裔男子發表仇恨言論，要求對方道歉和賠償。該男子涉嫌於上月一場「黑人的命也是命」（Black Lives Matter）遊行中，以種族字眼出言侮辱，並挑釁一名正在執勤的亞裔探員，整個過程被探員的隨身攝錄機拍下。<br />\n<br />\n訴訟周二在曼哈頓最高法院提出，被告哈珀（Terrell Harper）涉嫌在3月11日一場示威活動中，持續騷擾一名警察，稱他為「該死的吃貓者」並質疑他雙眼視力，對該名警察造成精神創傷。根據警探工會公開的短片，哈珀對鏡頭說，「你要用柔道劈我嗎？我不x怕你」。他又不斷以嘲諷語氣，重複說「醬油」；又說「去x一隻狗，然後在你媽媽面前烹調和吃掉牠。」<br />\n<br />\n....<br />\n<br />\n案中事主是曼哈頓華埠的市警五分局亞裔探員張立勇（Vincent Cheung），他表示提出訴訟主要目的，是希望對方道歉，而無論最終得到賠償金額多少，他都計劃全數捐到支援亞裔或反仇恨亞裔的組織。<br />\n<br />\n....<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210422/VE37ALSOBREAFNZADEHSFYEI3I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210422%2FVE37ALSOBREAFNZADEHSFYEI3I%2F&d=tbI6yIPhVaIexgVZB5ClnSPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=f2a987c1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210422%2FVE37ALSOBREAFNZADEHSFYEI3I%2F&h=7041ec79\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210422/VE37ALSOBREAFNZADEHSFYEI3I/</a>"},{"pid":"cbba471cb010331968bdd93cde985b1ff5041ee5","tid":2499673,"uid":119450,"like":66,"dislike":1,"score":65,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T05:26:13.000Z","msg":"Race War"},{"pid":"fde717e005a9e416c9494682216b7714234d1f2d","tid":2499673,"uid":88032,"like":137,"dislike":2,"score":135,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T05:27:17.000Z","msg":"竟然係Cheung而唔係Zhang<br />\n<br />\n上一代可能係嚟自香港"},{"pid":"ebe1e12c03319efff1c6be4bd6fdaac968c6aac0","tid":2499673,"uid":142965,"like":87,"dislike":2,"score":85,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T05:27:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https: